# Cloud Storage Best Practices

## Bucket Configuration

1. **Lifecycle and Versioning:**
   - Set appropriate lifecycle policies
   - Enable versioning if needed

2. **Naming:**
   - Use descriptive bucket names
   - Follow cloud provider naming conventions
   - Use variables for bucket names (don't hardcode)

